# 👨‍🏫 Mentor's Note

Today you learned something many first-time founders overlook: **a great app is not just functional—it must also be trustworthy.**

For a Blood Report Analyzer, users are sharing some of their most personal information. Features like AI explanations and report history are valuable, but they only matter if users feel confident that their data is safe.

